althcare M&amp;A practice positioning documented. $3.25M Conventional close in 44 days. <strong>The pattern: business broker brings deal cycle commission variability + retainer hybrid + sector specialty complexity, Stairway brings B3-3.1-01 extended averaging + B3-3.2-01 Form 1084 + IBBA certification narrative + continuity narrative craft to produce clean qualifying.</strong></p>
